snippet.title: Starcats Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Starcats is a party game where cooperation is a strategy, not a requirement. Activate generators to refuel your ship and escape the planet, but beware! Your fellow crew members can and will leave you stranded on the planet. 

Built in Unreal Engine 4, Starcats is a 2-4 player local couch game for PC, available on the Steam Store May 16th, 2018. 

https://store.steampowered.com/app/724920/Starcats/

Follow us on Twitter @StarcatsGame, or head to www.starcatsgame.com to learn more.
